reviewText: has some good stuff for the wanna be tig welder that you don't find on most U tube clips but I have to add that for 22.95 i was expecting just a smidge more of the good stuff and that is keeping from wanting to buy the second installment which ,now that i can see the value of it, has a cost/ benefit ratio that is pricing me out of the market  or at least take a deep breathe, exhale and give it some thought
